data.description: OPEN HOUSE SUN APRIL 14  12:00 - 2:00 PM      Welcome home to this newly refreshed two level condo.  Enter this large ground floor end unit condo features plenty of natural light, new carpet, fresh paint, and updated baths .   Open floor plan with 9ft+ ceilings,  Gourmet kitchen features stainless, granite & big breakfast bar! Huge primary suite w/his/her walk-in closets & luxury bath w/oversized shower! Attached garage plus add'l assigned space.   Terrific location right next to Owings Mills Town Center provides easy access to Costco, grocery store, shops & restaurants!  Easy to hop onto 795 makes your commute a breeze.  All exterior maintenance covered by condo!  Compare to nearby new construction selling over $400K for similar floorplans.
